		userDao<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">saveUser</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
	<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>创建接口UserDao</p>
<div class="language-java ext-java line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token keyword">public</span> <span class="token keyword">interface</span> <span class="token class-name">UserDao</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
